2D Top-Down RPG (Unity)
- A work-in-progress 2D top-down RPG built with Unity.

Current Features
- Player movement system
- Health system

Project Status

- This project is currently in active development. More features  and improvements will be added over time.

Built With

- Unity (2D)

Planned Features
- Combat system
- Enemies & AI
- Inventory system
- Dialogue system
- Level design & world building